data.description: Unwind in luxury at this exquisite real estate offering! Experience the epitome of private indulgence with your own gunite in-ground saltwater-heated pool, accompanied by a stunning pool house. This versatile space, used as a game room, gym, studio, etc…. Embrace the grandeur of large pillars that beautifully complement the pool area. Entertain in style with an open corner pavilion, featuring a captivating floor to ceiling brick wood-burning fireplace. Outdoor full bath included too! Your oasis of relaxation and entertainment awaits.   Step inside through the grand two-story entryway of this home. A motorized, massive chandelier adds a touch of opulence, ready to be raised or lowered at your command. The focal point of the entryway, coupled with the main staircase, sets the tone for the distinguished elegance within.  Indulge in the main level's exquisite offerings, including a separate dining area, a well-appointed office, and a spacious great room with plenty of built-ins. Bask in the warmth of the gas fireplace and open French doors that lead to your private oasis. This harmonious blend of functionality and luxury creates an inviting living space.  This home’s interior redefines luxury with a gourmet kitchen showcasing newer Monogram gas stove, newer Viking cabinet microwave, and an oversized Viking refrigerator. The kitchen invites gatherings with ample seating, featuring a cozy breakfast area and a stylish island.  The details shine, from the elegant copper sink to the exquisite granite countertops and backsplash. Organize with ease and enjoy the convenience of ample space for all your culinary essentials with an array of cabinets and a pantry.   The laundry room, conveniently located off the kitchen, boasts ample cabinets, a dedicated folding area, and features the latest Speed Queen washer and dryer. Enjoy the luxury of heated floors extending seamlessly from the kitchen to the laundry area.  The second level includes four bedrooms and a bonus room. The master suite is a haven featuring a walk-in closet with organizers and a sumptuous bath. Indulge in the opulence of heated Travertine tile floors, a towel rack, a signature jetted tub, a walk-in marble shower, and a marble countertop with double bowl sinks. This level also offers an open family room, connected by a second staircase leading down to the kitchen.  Explore the lower level, an entertainment haven! Unwind in the large theater room equipped with a newer projector and all the necessary equipment. Discover convenience in the second kitchen, featuring a huge Subzero refrigerator and a second microwave. This level also offers a full bath, an additional room perfect for various uses, and a third family room. Every detail has been carefully curated to ensure an exceptional living experience throughout the entire home.   The attached and detached garages boast stylish heated tile floors. The attached garage has a brand-new garage door and opener.
